{"tid":1459600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［機場發夢第二步］喬裝旅客行動正式啟動","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T18:28:19.000Z","uid":9824,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ada52511d0bc56c115b150a145eaba3dcedb3ba0","tid":1459600,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"轉：<br />\n標題： ［機場發夢第二步］喬裝旅客行動正式啟動<br />\n<br />\n琴日發夢去左機場 癱瘓左機場運作 <br />\n算是第一步成功左 <br />\n<br />\n要行第二步了 應該點樣繼續發個好夢呢<br />\n<br />\n頭先我又食藥訓覺<br />\n我夢見機場每日輪流都幾萬人迫爆 <br />\n呢幾萬人扮成旅客 冇人著黑衫 冇人衝擊 <br />\n警犬跟本分唔到旅客定發夢人士<br />\n冇人被捕 冇人受傷 但經濟繼續癱瘓 <br />\n原來最大既人質就係機場<br />\n<br />\n1. 請喬裝成旅客 拎警犬冇權力驅散<br />\n2. 請持之以恆 每日輪流去發夢癱瘓航空<br />\n3. 文宣組繼續出文 推廣發夢計劃2.0<br />\n<br />\n請大家推post 同share此方案<br />\n犬隻可以喬裝 我地都可以喬裝<br />\n<br />\n以卵擊石 只能敗走"},{"pid":"85979cd2429bcae54a9f8a5d18583be9111be0b2","tid":1459600,"uid":120308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:21:54.000Z","msg":"咩喬裝 我地係真旅客 去imax姐"},{"pid":"686c9dc5837957ef9bbe2556f2fe7b593ce27375","tid":1459600,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"[最後通諜]流水抗爭已到樽頸，下一升級必長佔機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457467</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"32e945cf3dd1d81a406b836d823222c4916fb347","tid":1459600,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:26:01.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgXWuUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgXWuUM.jpg&h=6e8aad15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://we.tl/t-zkYuY8ShZJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-zkYuY8ShZJ&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2z%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=459331da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-zkYuY8ShZJ</a>"},{"pid":"68628b94de2bdc921f1477c08a0320999dad391a","tid":1459600,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":